<!-- ============================================ -->
<!-- PRIORITY GUIDELINES -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<!--
1.0 - Homepage
0.9 - Key landing pages, pricing
0.8 - Main sections, blog index, product index
0.7 - Category pages
0.6 - Individual posts/products
0.5 - Less important pages
0.3 - Archive pages, tags
-->

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!-- CHANGEFREQ OPTIONS -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<!--
always   - Updates constantly
hourly   - Updates every hour
daily    - Updates daily
weekly   - Updates weekly
monthly  - Updates monthly
yearly   - Updates yearly
never    - Archived content
-->

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!-- NOTES -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<!--
- Maximum 50,000 URLs per sitemap
- Maximum 50MB file size (uncompressed)
- Use sitemap index for larger sites
- Can use gzip compression (.xml.gz)
- Submit via Google Search Console
- Reference in robots.txt
- lastmod should reflect actual content changes
-->
